OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDoctors warning about      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fweight loss surgery        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Foverseas                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Doctors have issued a warning over the 
OL,6, dangers of obese Scots travelling      
OL,7, abroad for weight loss surgery.        
OL,9,FOne firm said patients feel they cannot
OL,10,Fwait for the NHS to help them tackle   
OL,11,Fobesity and is flying about 60 people a
OL,12,Fmonth from Scotland to Turkey.         
OL,14,FBut surgeons say the health service is 
OL,15,Fleft to pick up the pieces when        
OL,16,Foperations or the aftercare goes wrong.
OL,18,FOne in 25 Scots is considered to be    
OL,19,Fseverely obese, one of the highest     
OL,20,Frates in Europe.                       
